{"tid":2063771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民協決定推薦施德來及何啟明出選9月立法會選舉","createTime":"2020-06-14T09:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T10:00:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b69110f25c60c77d2ffb5d007f4f6dc98edadbe5","tid":2063771,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1532009_1_L_20200614170447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1532009_1_L_20200614170447.jpg&h=897ea0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民協決定推薦主席施德來及副主席何啟明，準備出選9月立法會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n兩人本身分別為黃大仙及深水埗區議員，施德來會備選九龍東，何啟明則備選九龍西。施德來表示，已參與抗爭者表明當選後否決預算案的聯署，不會因擔心喪失參選資格而放棄聯署，又期望民主派九龍東的議席「坐三望四」。<br />\n<br />\n何啟明就認為，有意參選立法會的民主派應參加初選，組成最佳組合出選，而非等初選隊伍喪失參選資格後才加入戰團。"},{"pid":"155c636c30e899264caff0eadfe7ca0378915926","tid":2063771,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"九龍東「坐三望四」?發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72a911df50f9d1faca07a72a2b6700ddab2dd6d","tid":2063771,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:30:04.000Z","msg":"Btw民協竟然唔派人選超區?"},{"pid":"f9897a489b18fddb61aa3076139eb0264acdcc27","tid":2063771,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:30:26.000Z","msg":"唔初選根本冇意思"},{"pid":"63852e521bfac325c4e5486b1634a6cdbdb7b28f","tid":2063771,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"衛我城?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暗獨?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3317e181e20c59a3e6b869adf5c42d4caa191293","tid":2063771,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63852e521bfac325c4e5486b1634a6cdbdb7b28f","tid":2063771,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"